headline: CoStar Group Completes Acquisition of Domain, Ushering in a New Era of Innovation for Australia’s Property Market
summary: SYDNEY & ARLINGTON, Va., August 27, 2025--CoStar Group, Inc. (NASDAQ: CSGP), a leading provider of online real estate marketplaces, information, analytics and 3D digital twin technology in the property markets, announced today the successful completion of its acquisition of Domain Holdings Australia Limited ("Domain"), one of Australia’s leading property marketplaces.
